came away with many shiny new bits for those that had good luck.  All in all we took 54 people up and had over 30 of them still up at the end of the night.<br>
<br>
We encountered the Maestro's Hand and then found that an Unpleasant Hand is unpleasant.  <br>
<br>
We travelled up to the second floor and had our first encounter with new MOB's of Hate.  Yay fine steel weapons for loot again <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
<br>
Mistress of Scorn, Corrupter of Life, and the Ashenbone Broodmother are some of the other new spawns we encountered.  The joy of CH MOB's and the rampage attack. I think this rampage might actually be similiar to a melee disclpine.  <br>
<br>
I will be able to post a list of loot and winners in near future.<br>
<br>
Special thanks to those that helped make the raid successful, my management team, group leaders, Zellex and Vaard.  Without your support this would not have been nearly as successful or smooth. <br>
<br>
We had a couple of CR sessions this night and we did a good quick job of it.  I saw that people remained patient during each one and that helped us huge.  Thanks to the people dragging, the clerics with their work and mages, necros and enchanters pitching in as well. Good work on that, especially when we all got killed off that once.  <br>
